The elegantly shaped  stainless steel vacuum milk container is a practical addition for all lovers of milk specialities. Thanks to its familiar tried-and-tested principle  it holds 0.6 litres / 20 oz. and keeps the milk cool throughout the day.

The Milk Frother is the quick  easy  no-mess way to make perfect  velvety-soft milk foam for cold drinks such as latte frio  cold chocolate and many other popular specialities. Designed in line with JURA's classic style  it's the perfect addition to any coffee machine and an indispensable aid for all lovers of speciality beverages. Easy to operate using a single button  it prepares cold  warm or hot milk foam in a flash.   The perfect recipe for a wide range of speciality drinks  Cold  warm or hot milk foam  Easy one-button operation  High-quality  elegant and easy to clean

The popular speciality coffees of today would be unthinkable without fresh  cold milk. And to make sure this is available whenever it's needed  JURA has further developed the tried-and-tested Cool Control.  The Cool Control cools the milk to as much as 25° below the ambient temperature. Once the temperature reaches 4°C  it is maintained constantly within the optimum range. The Cool Control now comes with an energy-saving automatic switch-off function. When the stainless steel container is removed  the cooling function is automatically deactivated.  The high-quality stainless steel container holds 1 litre. With its bayonet lock  it is easy to remove  open  fill  store in the refrigerator as needed  and clean in the dishwasher.

Features/Description: Think of our Hudsons as part Explorer and part Earth Cruiser. Capable but cool. Casual but on it. We blended the flowing curves and shaped tubes of seemingly disparate platforms like our carbon Dakota 29’ers and our aluminum DXT’s and and came up with a smart frame design that rides comfortably  casually and efficiently while making a bold statement all at the same time.

Building great recreational-level bikes that ride much like (and look a lot like) our hi-end bikes is a passion at Jamis. And no bikes showcase our commitment to do just that better than these bikes. The Trail X chassis emphasizes all-day performance so the ride position isn’t as extreme as on our racing ATBs  the handling’s quick and sure without being overly darty. But make no mistake  if you want to throw down  the Trail X is more than able to keep up with precise shifting drivetrains and incredibly powerful disc or linear pull brakes.

The Vulture features the famous Grim Reaper “E” logo cutout in the headtube. It has a low slung frame for riders who prefer a low stand over height. We know it isn’t for everyone  but dang it sure makes learning whips easier. It’s loaded with great specs like a sealed bearing integrated headset  Eastern 3-piece tubular chromoly Throttle cranks  fully sealed rear hub  a fat seat and 25-9 microdrive gearing. You can rest easy with your new investment. When your skills advance and you are ready to step it up  use our Frame Upgrade program and get pro level products for a fraction of the cost. That’s the Eastern promise and our commitment to Eastern riders everywhere.

Fitness is about more than just exercise  so get the whole picture with this Black Flex Wireless Activity Wristband from Fitbit. It tracks a wide range of things  from calories burned to hours slept  so you can stay informed about your body and keep up with your fitness goals.   Multi-Tracking  This Flex wristband tracks all kinds of data about your fitness  including steps taken  calories burned  distance travelled  active minutes  hours slept and even the quality of your sleep. It helps you get the full picture when it comes to your body.  Stats Syncing  It couldn’t be easier to sync the data collected by this wireless activity wristband with your iPhone  Android device or computer. Simply copy your stats across via Bluetooth and you can review your stats whenever or wherever you want.  Set Goals  Complete the goals you set by staying up to date using this Fitbit wristband. It allows you to set fitness goals for the day and then will update you on your progress via a simple LED light system – so it’s easy to see at a glance how much you’ve done.  Simple Tough Design  The Flex has a simple design that won’t get in the way or be too bulky  keeping it simple and sleek so you can forget you’re even wearing it. The Flex is also water-resistant and has a silent wake up alarm - making it easier for you to get up in time for your morning run.

Product Name: Fitness GPS Watch - Entry Level 010-01039-00 Black/Red
Features/Description: Keep track of your run with the incredibly easy to use Forerunner 10 GPS running watch from Garmin. Its streamlined design lets you start your run with just one press of a button  and it accurately tracks your distance  speed/pace and calories. You can even see exactly how far you've gone and how fast you're running.    Stay Motivated  The Garmin Forerunner 10 makes the perfect training partner  with a range of alerts and statistics to keep you informed about your run. It automatically alerts you whenever you complete a mile  and after you save a run you can see a summary of how you did – including total distance  time  average pace and a calories burned. It even tracks your personal records  like your fastest mile travelled or longest run to date.  Training Tools  Need the extra edge on your training? This Forerunner 10 GPS watch has several useful training features which can help you train your body for competition or greater fitness levels. These include the Virtual Pacer™ which allows you to set a target pace and compare your current rate to your goal. There's also a handy run/walk feature so you can include walk breaks into your running plan.  Garmin Connect™  For even more information about your run or to share your records with friends  try uploading your runs to Garmin Connect™. Simple connect your Forerunner GPS watch to a Mac or PC and upload your recorded run to see your track on a map  get more detail on each mile or easily share it with your friends via social media. You can even track stats over time  so you can see how you've improved weekly  monthly or annually.

Product Name: Swim Watch-records laps  Strokes distance  Time
Features/Description: The Garmin Swim does the hardwork for you so you can stop counting laps. The Garmin Swim records your times  track your distance  pace and stroke count  but it can even sense your stroke and calculate your SWOLF score so that you can measure your swimming efficiency.    Ready to Go  Simply strap the Garmin Swim on your wrist  tell it a few details about the size of the pool and dive in.  Design  The rugged housing ensures that the Garmin Swim is water resistant to 50m. It is a slim  lightweight and stylish watch  in or out of the pool. When the battery runs low  you can replace it yourself  about once a year.  Record Features  The Garmin Swim has the capability to not only track your time and distance  but also your stroke and SWOLF score  so you can know how efficient your swimming is. Plus  it has a few different features such as drills and timed intervals  so that it can track whatever type of swimming you want.  Motivational Display  The Garmin Swim also serves as a reminder to keep on training  with a weekly accumulated swimming distance visible under the time of day. So  if you choose to double it up as a normal wristwatch you will be reminded to keep heading back to the pool.  Workout Analysing  After your workouts  download the data wirelessly to your computer and let Garmin Connect provide you with free online analysis  doubling as your interactive online logbook. View time  distance  stroke type  pace  cadence  stroke count  calories burned and more for a length  an interval or your entire workout. Garmin Connect also shows your efficiency/swolf score as recorded by your watch.

The P530 is the compact camera for those who demand superior quality and control. With an ultra-powerful 42x optical zoom and 84x Dynamic Fine Zoom  this camera offers super-telephoto shooting in a compact body. Its advanced 16.1-megapixel CMOS captures incredible detail and colour. Night photography is made possible by its maximum ISO sensitivity of 6400. Capture the action up close in amazing details with the 42x optical zoom lens. For even more extreme close-ups  the P530 features an 84x Dynamic Fine Zoom.  Brilliant shots day and night Capture sun-drenched days and sparkling nights with ease. With a maximum ISO sensitivity of 6400  the P530 delivers breathtaking clarity and vivid colours in a wide range of lighting conditions. Among the P530’s many Scene Modes  you’ll find the unique Moon Mode. This innovative function lets you capture sharp super-telephoto shots of the moon – a high-contrast shot that many cameras simply cannot capture. If you’re a bird lover  use the fast and precise Bird-Watching Mode to shoot close-ups of wild birds in action.  Ready when you are Never miss the moment again. Its fast autofocus takes as little as 0.20 seconds to lock on to your subject. For fast-paced action  the P530 features continuous shooting of up to 7 frames per second at maximum resolution.  Unshakeable quality Achieve crisp images while shooting in motion or at full zoom  thanks to its high-performance lens-shift Vibration Reduction (VR) and ACTIVE mode. Used together  these functions reduce camera shake so well that they produce an effect similar to a shutter speed that is 3.5 stops faster. This means optimum sharpness for your photos and videos.  Special occasions deserve Full HD The P530 records true-to-life Full HD videos in 1080p/60i format and with stereo sound. While recording  a precise autofocus ensures perfectly sharp subjects. You can even create a high-quality still image from a video frame.  Bring your imagination to life Get creative with the P530’s wide range of Special Effects and Filter Effects. In addition to being dust-proof  the camera is also cold resistant up to -10°c  so there’s nowhere the Nikon AW120 can’t go.  Versatility at its finest From underwater shots to night landscapes or dimly-lit environments  the wide-angle f/2.8 NIKKOR lens captures the ideal amount of light for a great picture. With a 5x optical zoom (covering 24mm to 120mm equivalent in 35mm format)  and a Dynamic Fine Zoom* (approximately 240mm equivalent in 35mm format)  it gives you the flexibility to capture faraway objects. Refined in performance The 16 megapixel lens  superb image-processing engine EXPEED C2  and backside illumination CMOS sensor all combine to give you bright  stunning and blur-free images. The target finding autofocus (AF) automatically hones in on the subject  while the Pre AF achieves focus even without pressing the shutter-release button halfway. The Pre-AF also activates immediately when a shake is detected  which means you just have to focus on what you want to shoot while the Nikon AW120 takes care of the rest.  The Nikon AW120 comes with built-in GPS  an electronic compass and a world map so you can lose yourself in what you’re doing without losing your way. The GPS also lets you log in the altitude/water depth and keep track of it at regular intervals. The built-in Wi-Fi® allows sharing moments instantly with your loved ones. Using the Wireless Mobile Utility App (available for download at the App Store and Google Play)  you can turn your smart phone to a remote shooting device  so you can be in the picture  with the vastness of nature as the perfect backdrop. The Record Pause feature of the Nikon AW120 lets you omit any action you don’t need in your movies just by pressing the pause button  and resume recording later with the same movie file. The traditional game resized to giant proportions! Our Giant Tumble Tower consists of 56 beautifully-crafted pine blocks  building a 19 level tower of 90cm at the start of the game. Once the Giant Tumble Tower is built players take turns to remove blocks from the tower and place on the top. The aim is to build the tower as high as possible using only one hand and without making the tower tumble! It is possible to build to over 150cm!  The Giant Tumble Tower set by Uber includes:  56 pine blocks measuring 21cm x 7cm x 4.7cm  Nylon transport/storage bag   Please note care should be taken when playing Giant Tumble Tower. Players should always be on their feet and be wary of the tower falling. Children should always be supervised.

Bring the fun of skittles to your home! The aim of this traditional bowling game is to knock all the skittles down with as few attempts as possible. Skittles is a fantastic game for players of all ages. This beautifully-crafted game is constructed from polished hardwood.  The Skittles set includes:  10 Hardwood Skittles each measuring 23cm in height with diameter of 5cm at base and 8cm in belly  the lead skittle has a red top.  3 Regulation balls 8cm in diameter  Canvas transport / storage bag
